                setup:
                disable file manager's automount to prevent interference (if applicable)
                $ cp /usr/local/share/usb-automount/usb-automount.conf ~/.config/
                edit ~/.config/usb-automount.conf (set your gui file manager)
                $ usb-automount &

                to remove a mounted device (menu will be presented if there is >1):
                $ usb-unmount [eject]
